<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0473013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473013">〔佛說〕－【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0473014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473014">一＝一之二【宋】【元】【宮】，明作十八卷九卷</note>
<note n="0473015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473015">譯經＝中天竺【元】＊，宋中天竺【明】＊</note>
<note n="0473016" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473016">〔沙門臣〕－【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0473017" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473017">等＝共法護【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0473018" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473018">（第四）＋譯【元】＊</note>
<note n="0473019" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473019">於＝于【明】下同</note>
<note n="0473020" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0473020">歡＝觀【明】</note>
<note n="0474001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0474001">邪＝耶【宋】【元】下同</note>
<note n="0474002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0474002">婆＝媻【明】＊</note>
<note n="0475001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0475001">唯＝惟【明】</note>
<note n="0475002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0475002">下＝四【宮】</note>
<note n="0476001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0476001">所＝是【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0476002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0476002">不分卷，〔佛…譯〕五十九字－【元】【明】</note>
</p>
